Last SIAs conducted in the country
DR Congo: last SIA was in July 2012, targeting 80/503 districts in the country. In addition, corrective rounds were organised in 2013 and 2014 in 75 of these districts
Chad: last SIAs occurred in 2014 and 2015. From 2014 to January 2015 a first SIA occurred in 35/84 districts of the country. In 2015 two rounds of another SIA took place in 46/84 other districts.
Nigeria: The last activity happened in October 2014, targeting 62/774 districts of the country. A campaign was organised in May 2016.
Ethiopia: 4/817 districts were targeted in a campaign that occurred in summer 2015. It was the 3rd round of an activity that started in 2012.
Pakistan: Last activity done was in September 2013.
